description.en: Offers instruction for people who need to acquire the basic skills and tools that are required to successfully apply for and secure employment, and retain a position once they have been hired. These programs offer information and guidance regarding preparing a resume, writing job application letters, completing job application questionnaires, responding to job ads and taking employment tests.  The programs may also offer tips regarding appropriate dress, personal appearance and interview techniques.
